{"tid":1234093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下一個主戰場-議會議席","createTime":"2019-06-17T00:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T03:06:28.000Z","uid":128594,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"edbab26ed23fe5285373b756996ac6c351263393","tid":1234093,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:37:42.000Z","msg":"我相信就算經過200萬人上街要求撤回送中，政府都係唔會開宗明義撤回議案，只會無限期拖延<br />\n<br />\n點解政府可以係呢一刻仲可以顧全所謂既管治威信唔撤回法案，就係因為背後有一班盲撐既保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n所以，趁民意未消，宜家要開始進行選舉工程，慢慢將保皇黨盲撐賣港法案既意識係市民心目中進行整固<br />\n<br />\n假設200萬人入面有8成係登記選民/符合選民登記資格，呢度所有票數足以令保皇黨失去大部分議席。<br />\n<br />\n只有透過控制立法會，令政府施政癱瘓，先可以威脅到政府要正面回應民意，而唔係擺出一副高高在上既嘴臉<br />\n<br />\n記住，得民心得天下"},{"pid":"758b82da1b5aff15e9faedc60b31f0321419b24c","tid":1234093,"uid":124282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:39:41.000Z","msg":"之前明明話射落海，焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ec74ccb98dde2d0401b7e4f0b985e9d217dbb0","tid":1234093,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:41:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7a7f6052eceeeca99ca4e009c62980cc4321583","tid":1234093,"uid":118344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ec74ccb98dde2d0401b7e4f0b985e9d217dbb0","tid":1234093,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:41:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:43:04.000Z","msg":"當年又話政府讓步機會底"},{"pid":"203ff88dbc79338e8fa8a342d9434646a4dc156d","tid":1234093,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:43:15.000Z","msg":"Dq你老母"},{"pid":"c22825be61d2015d986cbe5a9582ea9f564e75ec","tid":1234093,"uid":134174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"功能組別點贏？"},{"pid":"74a848c18ebe49d2153a88a38fd3d3680ff02002","tid":1234